data.message: young sculler wit a neck tie, i hold my head high, right before its bed time, dont hate me for my best rhymes, i've bin fly why am i cool, answering questions since high school. always makin wise moves, police chasin my crew, bullies wastin my food, rollies makin my doobz, the only place is my pool;-where i get the chills, wheres my record deal, burn out rubber wheels, its my turn now to come as real. feelings "none i feel" dealing wit the field
